{
  "stem": "12447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His name was Sokolowski.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was a streetcar conductor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Actually, he was an operator, one of the streetcar operators that ran Prague, Warsaw, on certain lines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- they had no children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were basically about the same age with my parents, maybe a little bit younger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they socialized with these two neighbors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I recall them very well, especially the one next door to us, Dombrowski, which-- they were good friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So as we go on later on in the war years, they helped me quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell me what led up to the war years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I can recall, in 1939, for example, my father was-- he was an invalid from World War I.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a glass eye and also had a, a scar on his hand-- I don't recall his right or his left hand.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was actually dreaming-- or maybe it was a reality-- that someday, as a invalid, he will be able to open a little tobacco stand or something like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That needed a, a license and some loan support from the government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were saving money for this particular purpose, that someday they'll be able to do that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father would not have to work in the factory-- he worked in a factory in the new town Praga, or they call it Nowa Praga.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was quite a distance for him to walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't think he was able to afford a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember he used to cross-- it was quite a bit of fields to walk between our building and the part that he worked.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had to walk through fields and then cross over, like, an embankment of a railroad running.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
